{"title":"他，作为书法家","authors":["廖志理"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"他，作为书法家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廖志理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧中国的墨砚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太多浓稠的苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太多激荡的愤怒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从韶峰起笔的一划"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅出神州第一缕霞光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸湘江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描出满山红叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伐井冈竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评述五千年史书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六盘山上　白云当纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁阵的诗行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将豪情引上了碧霄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔尖有时迂回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勾起大河上下漫天飞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻数点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅香又浮动了万里长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如雨泼墨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷雄师百万追穷寇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽兴狂草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国龙破壁穿空！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点成一枚国徽灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔如金水桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送五星红旗辉映未来！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}